==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unspell
<hw>Un*spell"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>spell</ets>.]</ety> <def>To break the power of (a
spell); to release (a person) from the influence of a spell; to
disenchant.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Such practices as these, . . . ⟦br⟧
The more judicious Israelites <qex>unspelled</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsphere</ent>⟦br⟧
